de.wirecard.epos.model.sale.request.carddata

Class EmvPtCardData

  • de.wirecard.epos.model.sale.request.carddata.EmvPtCardData
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    CardData, EmvCardData, HasEmvData, HasSignatureImg

    public class EmvPtCardData
implements EmvCardData

    This is a format of card data used by PosMate which sends track2 equivalent data encrypted (there is no SRED tag in EMV). The 'pan' parameter must be provided too because the switch doesn't know the plain text PAN.
